<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, viewport-fit=cover">
<meta name="theme-color" content="#0a0a0a" media="(prefers-color-scheme: dark)">
<meta name="theme-color" content="#ffffff" media="(prefers-color-scheme: light)">
<title>{{ title }}</title>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="{{ asset_prefix }}assets/style.css">
<link rel="manifest" href="{{ asset_prefix }}manifest.json">
<link rel="icon" href="{{ asset_prefix }}icon.svg" type="image/svg+xml">
<link rel="apple-touch-icon" href="{{ asset_prefix }}icon.svg">
<meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-capable" content="yes">
<meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-status-bar-style" content="default">
<meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-title" content="Daily News">
<script>
  if ('serviceWorker' in navigator) {
    window.addEventListener('load', () => {
      navigator.serviceWorker.register('{{ asset_prefix }}service-worker.js').catch(() => {});
    });
  }
</script>
</head>
<body>
<header class="site-header">
  <div class="header-inner">
    <h1 class="site-title">
      <a href="{{ home_href }}">📰 Daily News</a>
    </h1>
    <p class="date-line">{{ display_date }} 更新: {{ updated_at }}</p>
    <nav class="header-nav">
      {% if is_archive_page %}
        <a href="{{ home_href }}">最新</a>
      {% endif %}
      <a href="{{ asset_prefix }}archive/">アーカイブ</a>
    </nav>
  </div>
  <nav class="category-tabs">
    {% for cat in categories %}
      <a href="#{{ cat.key }}" class="tab">{{ cat.label }}</a>
    {% endfor %}
  </nav>
</header>

<main class="content">
  {% if daily_digest %}
    <section class="daily-digest">
      <h2 class="digest-title">📌 今日のポイント — {{ daily_digest.headline }}</h2>
      <ol class="digest-points">
        {% for point in daily_digest.points %}
          <li>{{ point }}</li>
        {% endfor %}
      </ol>
    </section>
  {% endif %}

  {% for cat in categories %}
    <section id="{{ cat.key }}" class="category">
      <h2 class="category-title">{{ cat.label }}</h2>
      {% if cat.articles %}
        <ul class="article-list">
          {% for article in cat.articles %}
            <li class="article-card" data-importance="{{ article.importance }}">
              <h3 class="article-title">
                <a href="{{ article.url }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">{{ article.title }}</a>
              </h3>
              {% if article.summary %}
                <p class="article-summary">{{ article.summary }}</p>
              {% endif %}
              <p class="article-meta">
                <span class="source">{{ article.source }}</span>
                {% if article.importance >= 4 %}
                  <span class="badge important">重要</span>
                {% endif %}
                <a class="external" href="{{ article.url }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">元記事 →</a>
              </p>
            </li>
          {% endfor %}
        </ul>
      {% else %}
        <p class="empty">このカテゴリの新着記事はありません。</p>
      {% endif %}
    </section>
  {% endfor %}
</main>

<footer class="site-footer">
  <p>各記事の著作権は元配信元に帰属します。要約は Claude API による自動生成です。</p>
  <p>使用モデル: <code>{{ model }}</code></p>
</footer>
</body>
</html>
